    <h2 class="heading">Getting Started</h2>

    <div class="faq-question">
      <h3>How do I create an account?</h3>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-answer">
      <p>To create an account, reach out to your administrative contact 
      from Stronger Educator with your preferred Google email address, as well as your Campus ID, 
      and District ID. They will create an account for you and then you can login with your Google email.
      </p>
      <p>
      Due to the privleged and sensitive student information that is processed, campuses and district accounts are only able to view their own district and campuses.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-question">
      <h3>How do I get started / How can I get in contact?</h3>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-answer">
      <p>Please visit <a href="https://www.strongered.com/who-we-are"> Stronger Educator </a> to set up appointment with Dr. Anthony Luevanos or through the company email stronger@strongered.com. </p>
    </div>
