  <div class="faq-section" id="account">
    <h2 class="heading">Account</h2>

    <div class="faq-question">
      <h3>How do I change my Login/password?</h3>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-answer">
      <p>Login for this website is secured through Google Authentication. If you have issues accessing your Google email account please reach out to the appropriate Google support services for assistance. 
      Here is a link for your convenience <a href="https://support.google.com/accounts/troubleshooter/2402620?hl=en"> Google Support Account Troubleshooting. </a>
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-question">
      <h3>How do I update my account information ?</h3>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-answer">
      <p>If your District or Campus Identifaciton information is incorrect, please notify the Stronger Educator admin team through the company email stronger@strongered.com. </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="faq-section" id="upload">
    <h2 class="heading">Uploading School Data</h2>

    <div class="faq-question">
      <h3>How do I upload data to be processed for my Campus/District?</h3>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-answer">
      <p>Navigate to the [Upload Data] button on the navigation bar.</p>
      <p>Download the template CSV file from our website.</p>
      <p>Locally through a CSV editing program such as Excel or Google Sheets, edit and paste in the corresponding information.</p>
      <p>Save the file locally and make sure it is in the ".csv" format, and then press the "Choose File" button and select the name of the .csv file you just saved</p>
      <p>Finally hit the "Import" button to process the upload.</p>

    </div>
  </div>

